net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.label: dnd5e_Util_assertLibVersion
net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.toolTip:
Utility to assert the current libversion of Lib:DnD5e is compatible. An optional parameter may be passed to assert this for any library token, as well. The entire macro code flow will abort should the version be incompatible.
arg(0)=required minimum version
arg(1)=(Optional) required maximum version; Use -1 to mean "no requirement"
arg(2)=(Optional) Token library to assert against
